text: Aike Visbeek (born 27 October 1976) is a Dutch cycling coach. He was team manager at Team Sunweb from 2013 to 2019,NU.nl, Ploegleider Visbeek: 'Het is zeldzaam dat plan zo goed werkt in Tour', 18 July 2017. Archived on 11 August 2020. team manager at SEG Racing Academy in 2020. In 2021 he started working with Intermarché-Wanty-Gobert Matériaux where he is performance manager.Aike Visbeek (Intermarché-Wanty-Gobert):”Van start met drie doelen”, wielerflits.nl, 24 June 2021. Archived on 1 July 2021. During the 2022 Tour de France, Visbeek was guest in the Dutch television program De Avondetappe on 8 July 2022.De Avondetappe met Danny Nelissen, Sven Nys en Aike Visbeek, NOS, 8 July 2022 ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Cycling coaches Category:Dutch cyclists
